videos.description: Florida State jumped out fast on Louisville after Dwayne Bacon hits a 3-pointer and on the next possession for the Seminoles, Xavier Rathan-Mayes hits the jumper as part of a 14-0 run.
videos.headline: Florida State starts off red-hot vs. Louisville
Louisville proves they're down but not out

videos.description: Florida State's Christ Koumadje slides into the lane to get the ball and throw down the monster slam.
videos.headline: Koumadje's slam leaves the rim shaking

videos.description: Florida State shows off the defense with a big block that starts the leak-out for Terance Mann who throws down the one-handed dunk getting the crowd, and Dick Vitale, fired up.
videos.headline: FSU block at one end turns into jam at the other

videos.description: FSU forces ball out-of-bounds off Tony Hicks's head to re-gain possession
videos.headline: FSU forces ball out-of-bounds off Tony Hicks's head to re-gain possession

videos.description: After Louisville claws all the way back to within a point of Florida State, the Seminoles answer right back including Xavier Rathan-Mayes draining a 3-pointer to push the lead back to six.
videos.headline: FSU answers Louisville surge with Rathan-Mayes 3-pointer

videos.description: Breaking down FSU's 73-68 win over Louisville
videos.headline: Breaking down FSU's 73-68 win over Louisville
